tweet: Randall “Ka Randy” Echanis spent his life in the struggle for just peace and genuine agrarian reform—for this, he was tortured and stabbed to death. We are Ka Randy. They tried to bury us. They didn’t know we are seeds. We ring the call: #StopKillingFarmers and #StopTheKillingsPH
name: Karapatan
